  questId: warden_charge
  title: The Warden's Charge
  giverName: The Warden
  offerText: "You there \u2014 new blood. The Bleak creeps closer each night and
    the watch grows thin. Prove your worth: bring me timber for the palisade, fletch
    your own arrows, and thin the goblin scouts massing in the Ashfields. Do that,
    and the hold will call you one of its own."
  activeText: The palisade won't raise itself, and those goblins still draw breath.
    Come back when the work is done.
  turnInText: "Timber, arrows, and goblin blood on the ash. You'll do. Take this
    \u2014 you've earned a place at the fire."
  objectives:
  - type: 0
    targetId: log_0
    required: 3
    label: Chop Rough Logs
  - type: 1
    targetId: arrows
    required: 1
    label: Fletch Arrows at the Bench
  - type: 2
    targetId: 
    required: 4
    label: Slay Goblins in the Ashfields
